{"tid":2330483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"歐洲議會通過決議推動《馬格尼茨基人權法》、「救生艇計劃」及暫援引渡協議","createTime":"2020-12-18T05:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T07:04:37.000Z","uid":28114,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0d91ac49232e16ea1a6f961f6d7c664e5a26b897","tid":2330483,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:12:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1457138397739962/posts/3463985593721889/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1457138397739962%2Fposts%2F3463985593721889%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=a1efd6f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1457138397739962/posts/3463985593721889/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Watch<br />\n🇪🇺 歐洲議會通過決議推動《馬格尼茨基人權法》、「救生艇計劃」及暫援引渡協議<br />\n<br />\n因應香港以及新疆（東突厥）的情況，歐洲議會於昨日以大比數604比20通過共同決議，推動《馬格尼茨基人權法》、「救生艇計劃」、並暫援歐盟國家以及中國之間的引渡協議。<br />\n<br />\n#國際制裁<br />\n於決議中，歐洲議會議員呼籲歐盟儘快運用早前落實的《馬格尼茨基人權法》制裁參與打壓民主自由的中國及香港官員。<br />\n<br />\n#救生艇計劃<br />\n香港監察於6月發起倡議活動推動國際救生艇計劃（<a href=\"https://www.hongkongwatch.org/international-lifeboat-campaign\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongwatch.org%2Finternational-lifeboat-campaign&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=8d426118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongwatch.org/international-lifeboat-campaign</a>），歐洲議會今日亦於協議中表示支持計劃，呼籲歐盟國家加入英國、加拿大、澳洲等國家透過移民、政治庇護、留學簽證等政策為香港人提供「安全港」。<br />\n<br />\n#暫援引渡協議<br />\n香港監察亦積極推動全球各國暫援與香港及中國的引渡協議（<a href=\"https://www.hongkongwatch.org/extradition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongwatch.org%2Fextradition&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=693bf2f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongwatch.org/extradition</a>），確保香港人、維吾爾族人、西藏人以及其他異見人士不會被引渡到中國受審。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會亦於是次協議中通過是項建議。"},{"pid":"048dca599e1a11ec9331386390d9b710f6ea4dde","tid":2330483,"uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:14:17.000Z","msg":"歐洲議會無實權<br />\n<br />\n要等個別成員國自行去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5615d771be30fcb4efb0281868122685dd6c3f0d","tid":2330483,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"048dca599e1a11ec9331386390d9b710f6ea4dde","tid":2330483,"uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:14:17.000Z","msg":"歐洲議會無實權<br />\n<br />\n要等個別成員國自行去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"依家歐洲仲有邊d國家未暫停同香港嘅引渡條例？"},{"pid":"6338bb4c6a717b17fb03471669b2ee5b9139b262","tid":2330483,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:19:58.000Z","msg":"歐洲，我黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拜拜啦，支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdcc8f92c6f6f7bb62066dcac6815842b55e2bb6","tid":2330483,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee98789e6cbf6537f3859abec3042eb04d77d113","tid":2330483,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5615d771be30fcb4efb0281868122685dd6c3f0d","tid":2330483,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"048dca599e1a11ec9331386390d9b710f6ea4dde","tid":2330483,"uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:14:17.000Z","msg":"歐洲議會無實權<br />\n<br />\n要等個別成員國自行去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"依家歐洲仲有邊d國家未暫停同香港嘅引渡條例？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:27:31.000Z","msg":"好似都7788<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd826a3166e9ebdb72260a31587dbcda8dab0212","tid":2330483,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":